---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Stove Philosophy | Leftovers">
  <main class="mx-auto min-h-screen max-w-5xl px-6 py-14 sm:py-20">
    <section>
      <p
        class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-slate-700 bg-slate-900/70 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium tracking-wide text-slate-300"
      >
        Memento Mori...tality of Leftovers
      </p>
      <h1
        class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl"
      >
        All food expires, including your emotional support cheese.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-300 sm:text-lg">
        Remember: all food expires. Even that which seems preserved will
        eventually spoil. This is not cause for despair, but urgency—eat the
        good cheese today, for tomorrow it may be fuzzy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">
          The Existential Fridge Door Moment
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
          We have all stared into the fridge at midnight, asking deep questions
          of a container labeled “sauce??”. Stove Philosophy says: label your
          leftovers and your intentions.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Urgency, Not Panic</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
          You do not need to sprint through life with a fork. You do need to
          stop postponing joy for a mythical future where your schedule is calm
          and your cilantro never wilts.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article
        class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5 sm:col-span-2"
      >
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">
          Tonight&apos;s Reminder
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">
          Text the friend. Take the walk. Use the fancy plate. Open the nice
          olive oil. Life is short, and leftovers are shorter.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
